    | **Wrap Up and Closing** | **Wrap Up and Closing (10 minutes)**<br>Debrief Questions:<br>• [Question connecting to the day's objectives]<br>• [Question previewing the next day's content]<br>Exit Ticket: [Quick assessment prompt tied to a key learning from today] |
    | **Instructor Tips** | **Instructor Tips**<br>• Subject Matter Focus: [Technical content emphasis for today]<br>• Teaching Strategy: [Pedagogical guidance for non-trained teachers]<br>• Safety Reminders: [If applicable — otherwise remove this line]<br>• Common Student Challenges: [Anticipated difficulties and solutions]<br>• Extension Opportunities: [Ideas for advanced learners] |

