    | **Activities:** | |
    | **Welcome and Introduction** | **Welcome and Introduction (10 minutes)**<br>Bell work prompt: [Write a question that previews today's main content and connects to learning objectives or reviews vocabulary]<br>Briefly introduce today's objective and agenda. |
