    | **ASSIGNMENT: [Title]** | **Assignment: [Descriptive Title] ([XX] minutes)**<br>• [Step-by-step instructor instructions aligned with student-facing storyboard instructions]<br>• [Indicate materials, tools, or resources from Blueprint]<br>• [Describe what students will submit or be evaluated on] |
